<label><<radiobutton "$sacrifice" 'ヒダマリ' autocheck>><img class="hidamari">ヒダマリ　</label>
<label><<radiobutton "$sacrifice" 'フシグモ' autocheck>><img class="fusigumo">フシグモ　</label>
